NASA WorldWind
 

Package gov.nasa.worldwind.util.layertree

Displays a list of layers using BasicTree. The layer tree also supports displaying a tree of KML features.

See LayerTreeUsage for an example of how to use the layer tree. See KMLViewer for an example of using the layer tree to display the contents of a KML document.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KMLContainerTreeNode
    A KMLFeatureTreeNode that represents a KML container defined by a KMLAbstractContainer.
    KMLFeatureTreeNode
    A TreeNode that represents a KML feature defined by a KMLAbstractFeature.
    KMLLayerTreeNode
    A LayerTreeNode that represents a KML feature hierarchy defined by a KMLRoot.
    KMLNetworkLinkTreeNode
    A KMLFeatureTreeNode that represents a KML network link defined by a KMLNetworkLink.
    LayerTree
    A Renderable tree of Layer objects and their content.
    LayerTreeModel
    A tree model representing Layer objects and their content.
    LayerTreeNode
    A TreeNode that represents a Layer.
